# Walkthrough: Repository Refactoring (Mongoose Isolation)

We have successfully refactored the entire project to strictly adhere to the Repository Pattern. All Mongoose-specific logic (`Types.ObjectId`, `$push`, `$pull`, `populate`, `toObject()`, aggregation pipelines) has been completely removed from the Service layers and encapsulated within the Repositories.

## The Goal
The primary objective was to make the Service layer **database-agnostic**. Services should not know that the underlying database is MongoDB or that the ORM is Mongoose. They should only deal with plain JavaScript objects and primitives (like `string` IDs).

## Modules Refactored

### 1. Quiz Module
The heaviest offender. We removed over 35 imports/uses of `Types.ObjectId` and Mongoose document types from [QuizService](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/nestjs/edu-vacation/src/modules/quiz/quiz.service.ts#19-356).
*   **Added to [QuestionRepository](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/nestjs/edu-vacation/src/DB/repository/question.repository.ts#8-40)**: [findByDifficultyAndScope](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/nestjs/edu-vacation/src/DB/repository/question.repository.ts#24-39)
*   **Added to [QuizRepository](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/nestjs/edu-vacation/src/DB/repository/quiz.repository.ts#8-42)**: [findByIdWithQuestions](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/nestjs/edu-vacation/src/DB/repository/quiz.repository.ts#24-28), [findByLessonId](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/nestjs/edu-vacation/src/DB/repository/quiz.repository.ts#29-33), [toggleHidden](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/nestjs/edu-vacation/src/DB/repository/quiz.repository.ts#34-41)
*   **Added to [QuizResultRepository](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/nestjs/edu-vacation/src/DB/repository/quiz-result.repository.ts#8-126)**: 10 distinct methods including complex aggregation pipelines (e.g., [getAverageByLesson](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/nestjs/edu-vacation/src/DB/repository/quiz-result.repository.ts#45-53), [findStudentAttemptsPopulated](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/nestjs/edu-vacation/src/DB/repository/quiz-result.repository.ts#90-101))
*   **Updated [QuizController](file:///c:/Users/user/Desktop/nestjs/edu-vacation/src/modules/quiz/quiz.controller.ts#24-171)**: Boundary conversion using `_id.toString()`.

